      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;castgarden-video&#34;&gt;CastGarden Video&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe title=&#34;Ubuntu Sway Remix 23.04 My New Daily Driver?&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; src=&#34;https://cast.garden/videos/embed/1beb6ca1-0b28-4186-86c1-f2fd3758d5e6&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; sandbox=&#34;allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;click-here-to-play-this-video-on-torhttpcastgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddydonionw4rxqrqxsmwjthksnbqktkc&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://castgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddyd.onion/w/4rXQRQxsmWjTHKSnBQKTKC&#34;&gt;Click here to play this video on Tor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Originally published June 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;I heard about this distro on The Linux Cast&amp;rsquo;s YouTube channel and tried it out. I am in love with this! I have it installed on 2 machines already and been daily driving it both at play &amp;amp; the day job.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
